column5: do you know the web site for d&e baits in ear falls... or any other bait stores on the way up from dryden thanks for your time jake

[font color=green size=3][b]D & E Minnows, Ear Falls Ont. 807-274-2074 That's an old number, Their website doesn't seem to be working. Rumor was they were running a resort in the area this year? There are other places, depending on what you are looking for. Wish'in I was fish'in on Wabby
